---
# `min` reports only fatal problems: parse errors, load failures, and playbook
# syntax errors. That is deliberately conservative — the base, users, k3s and
# tailscale roles predate any linting, and a stricter profile would fail CI on
# pre-existing style rather than on real defects.
#
# Tighten to `basic` once those roles have been cleaned up separately.
profile: min

exclude_paths:
  - inventory/
